            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20moment%20God%20promised%20the%20devil%20that%20Eve's%20offspring%20would%20crush%20his%20head%2C%20Satan%20sought%20to%20murder%20the%20Messiah.%20John%208%3A44%20tells%20us%20that%20%22he%20was%20a%20murderer%20from%20the%20beginning%20and%20has%20always%20hated%20the%20truth.%22%20The%20spirit%20of%20murder%20is%20of%20the%20devil.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EThinking%20that%20perhaps%20Abel%20was%20the%20Messiah%2C%20Satan%20incited%20Cain%20to%20murder%20his%20brother.%20Later%2C%20when%20he%20realized%20that%20Jesus%20was%20the%20true%20Messiah%2C%20he%20provoked%20the%20bloodthirsty%20tyrant%20Herod%20into%20killing%20%22all%20the%20boys%20in%20and%20around%20Bethlehem%20who%20were%20two%20years%20old%20and%20under%2C%20because%20the%20wise%20men%20had%20told%20him%20the%20star%20first%20appeared%20to%20them%20about%20two%20years%20earlier%22%20(Matthew%202%3A16).%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3ESatan's%20hatred%2C%20not%20only%20for%20Christ%20but%20also%20for%20those%20who%20are%20%22Christ-ians%2C%22%20has%20driven%20him%20to%20murder%20millions%20of%20believers%20worldwide.%20Try%20as%20he%20will%2C%20though%2C%20to%20gather%20those%20who%20will%20%22plot%20together%20against%20the%20Lord%20and%20against%20his%20anointed%20one%22%20(Psalm%202%3A2)%2C%20the%20devil%20is%20always%20defeated!%20In%20fact%2C%20God%20even%20laughs%20at%20Satan's%20anger%20and%20murderous%20attempts%20to%20stop%20His%20Son%20from%20redeeming%20the%20world%20(v.%204).%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20ultimate%20prophecy%20to%20believers%20will%20be%20fulfilled%3A%20%22Only%20ask%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20you%20the%20nations%20as%20your%20inheritance%2C%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20earth%20as%20your%20possession%22%20(v.%208).%20We%20are%20on%20the%20winning%20side!%3C%2Fp%3E"
        },
